# Grouper 0.9

TODO Sync with Basecamp

## Next Actions
* Review exceptions
  * Should MemberNotFound and SubjectNotFound be replaced by Runtime
    exceptions?  Or at least be used more selectively?
  * should PrivilegeNotFoundException and SchemaException be merged?
    * Or just remove PNFE?
* Implement STEM 
* _Stem_ child stems mapping
* _Stem_ parent stem mapping
  * _Group_ parent stem mapping
* Implement CREATE
* Group deletion when groups have members or are members
* Implement ADMIN
* Implement UPDATE
* Implement READ
* Implement VIEW

## Later
* Replace `_init()` methods with static {} declarations where possible
* Implement OPTIN
* Implement OPTOUT
* Implement remaining unimplemented methods
* Review generated SQL
  * Including my twisty column names
* Commons logging
* Review old _*.todo_ test classes
  * More effective membership testing
* Add create member and time to memberships
* Add create time to members
* Rename subjectIDs in local subject<=>member mapping (#133)
* many-to-many maping between _Field_ and _GroupType_
* Test concurrent mods and access
* What triggers a "modified" update?
* Profiling and benchmarking
* Custom group types
  * Map _GroupType_
* Custom group attributes
  * add to group subjects
  * query filters
  * setting, unsetting, nullable, etc
* Custom group lists
  * add to group subjects
* Additional query filters
* Update Subject API jar
* normalize source adapter id + name conventions
* wheel group
* record where each *Finder method is called from
* Review files and add TODO items to this list
* Test with Pg and Oracle and review generated SQL
* Update and expand query api javadocs
* Replace contrib with updated cdg
* Switch to Hibernate 3.x

